# React/Next.js Frontend Patterns

## Component Props

Luôn định nghĩa interface cho props; TUYỆT ĐỐI không dùng `any`:

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
function UserCard(props: any) {
  return <div>{props.name}</div>;
}

// ✅ GOOD
interface UserCardProps {
  user: User;
  onEdit?: (id: string) => void;
}

function UserCard({ user, onEdit }: UserCardProps) {
  return (
    <div>
      <h3>{user.name}</h3>
      {onEdit && <button onClick={() => onEdit(user.id)}>Edit</button>}
    </div>
  );
}
```

## State Management

- Server state: Use React Query (TanStack Query)
- Client state: Use Zustand

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Server state with React Query
import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query';

function UserList() {
  const { data, isLoading, error } = useQuery({
    queryKey: ['users'],
    queryFn: () => userService.getAll(),
  });
  // ...
}

// ✅ GOOD - Client state with Zustand
import { create } from 'zustand';

interface CartStore {
  items: CartItem[];
  addItem: (item: CartItem) => void;
}

const useCartStore = create<CartStore>((set) => ({
  items: [],
  addItem: (item) => set((state) => ({ items: [...state.items, item] })),
}));
```

## API Calls

Never call API directly in components, always use service layer:

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
function UserList() {
  useEffect(() => {
    fetch('/api/users').then(res => res.json());
  }, []);
}

// ✅ GOOD
// services/user.service.ts
export const userService = {
  getAll: async (): Promise<User[]> => {
    const response = await api.get<ResponseDto<User[]>>('/users');
    return response.data.data;
  },
};

// components/UserList.tsx
function UserList() {
  const { data } = useQuery({
    queryKey: ['users'],
    queryFn: userService.getAll,
  });
}
```

## Component Architecture

### Chia nhỏ component hợp lý

- Mỗi component chỉ làm 1 việc (Single Responsibility).
- Tách UI component (presentational) và logic component (container).
- Component nhỏ hơn 200 dòng; nếu lớn hơn → tách nhỏ.

```typescript
// ❌ BAD - Component quá lớn, làm nhiều việc
function ProductPage() {
  // 500+ dòng code với nhiều logic
}

// ✅ GOOD - Chia nhỏ
// components/product/ProductHeader.tsx
function ProductHeader({ product }: { product: Product }) { ... }

// components/product/ProductGallery.tsx
function ProductGallery({ images }: { images: string[] }) { ... }

// components/product/ProductInfo.tsx
function ProductInfo({ product }: { product: Product }) { ... }

// app/products/[id]/page.tsx
export default async function ProductPage({ params }: { params: { id: string } }) {
  const product = await getProduct(params.id);
  return (
    <div>
      <ProductHeader product={product} />
      <ProductGallery images={product.images} />
      <ProductInfo product={product} />
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Server Components vs Client Components

**Mặc định dùng Server Component** (không cần 'use client'). Chỉ dùng Client Component khi:
- Cần interactivity (onClick, onChange, useState, useEffect)
- Cần browser APIs (localStorage, window, document)
- Cần hooks (useState, useEffect, useContext)
- Cần event listeners

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Server Component (mặc định)
// app/products/page.tsx
export default async function ProductsPage() {
  const products = await getProducts(); // Fetch từ server
  return <ProductList products={products} />;
}

// ✅ GOOD - Client Component (cần interactivity)
// components/ProductCard.tsx
'use client';

import { useState } from 'react';

export function ProductCard({ product }: { product: Product }) {
  const [liked, setLiked] = useState(false);
  return (
    <Card onClick={() => setLiked(!liked)}>
      {product.name}
    </Card>
  );
}

// ✅ GOOD - Hybrid: Server fetch, Client interact
// app/products/page.tsx
export default async function ProductsPage() {
  const products = await getProducts(); // Server fetch
  return <ProductListClient products={products} />; // Pass data to client
}

// components/ProductListClient.tsx
'use client';
export function ProductListClient({ products }: { products: Product[] }) {
  const [filter, setFilter] = useState('');
  return <div>{/* Interactive UI */}</div>;
}
```

## Data Fetching Strategy

### SSR (Server-Side) - Ưu tiên cho:
- **SEO-critical data**: Product details, category pages, blog posts
- **Initial page load**: Homepage, product listing
- **Public data**: Categories, featured products, static content
- **User-agnostic data**: Không phụ thuộc user session

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - SSR cho SEO
// app/products/[id]/page.tsx
export default async function ProductPage({ params }: { params: { id: string } }) {
  const product = await getProduct(params.id); // Server fetch
  return <ProductDetails product={product} />;
}

// ✅ GOOD - SSR cho initial load
// app/page.tsx
export default async function HomePage() {
  const [featured, categories] = await Promise.all([
    getFeaturedProducts(),
    getCategories(),
  ]);
  return <HomePageClient featured={featured} categories={categories} />;
}
```

### CSR (Client-Side) - Dùng cho:
- **User-specific data**: Cart, wishlist, user profile (sau khi auth)
- **Real-time updates**: Notifications, chat, live data
- **Interactive filters**: Search, filters, pagination (sau initial load)
- **Heavy computations**: Charts, analytics (không block initial render)

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - CSR cho user data
'use client';
function UserCart() {
  const { data: cart } = useQuery({
    queryKey: ['cart'],
    queryFn: () => cartService.getMyCart(),
  });
  return <CartItems items={cart} />;
}

// ✅ GOOD - CSR cho filters (sau SSR initial)
'use client';
function ProductFilters({ initialProducts }: { initialProducts: Product[] }) {
  const [filters, setFilters] = useState({});
  const { data: filtered } = useQuery({
    queryKey: ['products', filters],
    queryFn: () => productService.search(filters),
    initialData: initialProducts, // Use SSR data as initial
  });
  return <ProductList products={filtered} />;
}
```

### Quy tắc chọn SSR vs CSR:

1. **Có thể SSR?** → Dùng SSR (tốt cho SEO, performance)
2. **Cần interactivity?** → Client Component với data từ Server
3. **User-specific?** → CSR sau khi auth
4. **Real-time?** → CSR với WebSocket/Socket.io

## Query Optimization

### Tối ưu React Query:

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Query key đúng, staleTime hợp lý
const { data } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ['products', categoryId, page], // Specific key
  queryFn: () => productService.getByCategory(categoryId, page),
  staleTime: 5 * 60 * 1000, // 5 phút cho data ít thay đổi
  gcTime: 10 * 60 * 1000, // Cache 10 phút
});

// ✅ GOOD - Parallel queries
const { data: products, data: categories } = useQueries({
  queries: [
    { queryKey: ['products'], queryFn: getProducts },
    { queryKey: ['categories'], queryFn: getCategories },
  ],
});

// ✅ GOOD - Prefetch cho navigation
const queryClient = useQueryClient();
const prefetchProduct = (id: string) => {
  queryClient.prefetchQuery({
    queryKey: ['product', id],
    queryFn: () => getProduct(id),
  });
};

// ❌ BAD - Query không tối ưu
const { data } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ['data'], // Key quá generic
  queryFn: fetchAll, // Fetch quá nhiều data
  staleTime: 0, // Luôn refetch
});
```

### Tối ưu Server Components:

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Parallel fetching
export default async function Page() {
  const [products, categories, banners] = await Promise.all([
    getProducts(),
    getCategories(),
    getBanners(),
  ]);
  return <HomePage products={products} categories={categories} banners={banners} />;
}

// ✅ GOOD - Selective data fetching
export default async function ProductCard({ id }: { id: string }) {
  const product = await getProduct(id, { 
    select: { id: true, name: true, price: true, image: true } // Chỉ fetch cần thiết
  });
  return <Card product={product} />;
}

// ❌ BAD - Sequential fetching
export default async function Page() {
  const products = await getProducts(); // Chờ xong
  const categories = await getCategories(); // Rồi mới fetch tiếp
  return <Page products={products} categories={categories} />;
}
```

## Performance Best Practices

### Checklist khi code component:

- [ ] **Component size**: < 200 dòng, nếu lớn → tách nhỏ
- [ ] **Server vs Client**: Mặc định Server Component, chỉ 'use client' khi cần
- [ ] **Data fetching**: SSR cho SEO/public data, CSR cho user-specific/real-time
- [ ] **Query keys**: Specific, không generic
- [ ] **Parallel fetching**: Dùng Promise.all() thay vì sequential
- [ ] **Selective fields**: Chỉ fetch data cần thiết (Prisma select)
- [ ] **StaleTime**: Set hợp lý (5-10 phút cho static data)
- [ ] **Prefetch**: Prefetch data khi hover vào link
- [ ] **Code splitting**: Dynamic import cho heavy components
- [ ] **Memoization**: useMemo/useCallback cho expensive computations

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Dynamic import
const HeavyChart = dynamic(() => import('./HeavyChart'), {
  loading: () => <Skeleton height={400} />,
  ssr: false, // Không cần SSR cho chart
});

// ✅ GOOD - Memoization
const expensiveValue = useMemo(() => {
  return computeExpensive(data);
}, [data]);

const handleClick = useCallback((id: string) => {
  onSelect(id);
}, [onSelect]);
```

